reviews.name: Charmed: The Complete Fifth Season (Full Frame)
reviews.reviewText: I was really excited to get season five; so were my daughters! We waited a whole week and were at the mailbox everyday. Our favorite episode was the last one where the sisters were goddesses. It was funny and so sad at the same time. We all cried when Piper lost Leo and we are anxious to see when she gets him back. Not to mention, I am waiting for my daughters to be able to find out who Chris really is. We enjoyed watching the Charmed Ones saga unfold. We are hoping to be able to purchase season six, asap.
reviews.title: I only have 3 more to go!

reviews.name: Charmed: The Complete Fifth Season (Full Frame)
reviews.reviewText:
Well I love charmed..I do...I mean if im willing to pay for the seasons that is pretty obvious that i love the show...its just that season five...liag...its been only about Phoebe...so far what ive watched anyway...i mean not even Wyat's birth seemed as special as it was becuase they were so focused on
Phoebe being the Mid Wife...that they didnt give enough attention to what mattered the most...I truly hope that the rest of the seasons are not all about Phoebe...i mean she is good i like her...but y'all just focused on Phoebe Phoebe Phoebe in season 5...what about Page who is BEAITUFUL!! N Piper who is an anwesome character....OMG IVE BEEN BLABBING A LONG TIME... SORRY...BUT SEASON 5 AINT ALL THAT GOOD...
